nvim --version: NVIM v0.5.0-dev+94cf7bb
Operating system/version: macOS 11.2
Terminal name/version: kitty
$TERM: xterm-256color

**Steps to reproduce using** 

Have the following config:

```lua
-- file: ~/.config/nvim/init.lua

